heading: Plucked instrument septets.
general-note: Here are entered collections of septets not in a specific form or of a specific type for various combinations of seven plucked stringed instruments. Individual plucked instrument septets and collections not in a specific form or of a specific type for a single combination of instruments are entered under this heading followed by the instruments in alphabetical order..
Collections of compositions for seven plucked keyboard instruments are entered under. Keyboard instrument ensembles; Harpsichord ensembles, and similar headings..
